## Phase 3: User Story 7 - Configure Database Connection (Priority: P1) 🎯 CRITICAL

**Goal**: Enable users to configure database connection settings before using the application

**Independent Test**: Run `linkmgr init`, provide database settings, verify config file is created and subsequent commands connect successfully

### Implementation for User Story 7

- [ ] T027 [US7] Create `internal/cmd/init.go` - Interactive configuration initialization command
- [ ] T028 [US7] Add interactive prompts for database host, port, user, password, database name
- [ ] T029 [US7] Test database connection during init and provide immediate feedback
- [ ] T030 [US7] Save validated configuration to ~/.linkmgr.yaml with appropriate file permissions (0600)
- [ ] T031 [US7] Add `--test-connection` flag to verify existing configuration
- [ ] T032 [US7] Add help text and examples to init command

